    "description": "Sin Survivor is a wave-based, first-person co-operative or single-player shooter based in a post-apocalyptic world overrun with blood-hungry, satanic demons.<br>Portals to hell have begun to spawn across the earth, with swarms of demons flooding the planet with the sole intention of destroying humanity. Your job is to halt evil in its tracks and attempt to close the portals to hell. You and your co-op team will explore maps by collecting keys and open doors from dead demons, purchasing weapons and bonuses from vending machines using your points generated by kills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503950/extras/6497309e862c3a31b3810eabf7055630.avif?t=1636158434\" width=620 height=346 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503950/extras/characters.PNG?t=1636158434\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503950/extras/b1a326010dd71368a8b170d2f26b91cc.avif?t=1636158434\" width=620 height=312 /></span><br><br>Waves of demons will be endless, but not without a twist. You will randomly experience ‘Swarm’ waves that will consist of small crawling demons that die easily but can quickly overpower any skilled gunman. You will also experience ‘The Darkness’. A wave dedicated to heightening your senses, where the lights will go out and using your trusted flashlight, giving you only a glimpse of the vision required to deal with the terror that awaits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503950/extras/98e65e222f991dec7c67c136ca4fec29.avif?t=1636158434\" width=620 height=268 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503950/extras/enemies.PNG?t=1636158434\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503950/extras/4d2a11c5ddf87e4d7bf6e07edd0c28db.avif?t=1636158434\" width=620 height=346 /></span><br><br>The game will have a character select and a levelling system for guns, clothing items and other accessories. As well as initial achievements and bonuses which will be regularly updated.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503950/extras/845937fad4337de5c119bfdd5861e492.avif?t=1636158434\" width=620 height=346 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503950/extras/5447bec76c78ac99e0f24931e1ed7c7f.avif?t=1636158434\" width=620 height=312 /></span>",
